1
00:00:03,450 --> 00:00:06,820
Why is one artwork selling
for a hundred million Euros,

2
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:10,182
and the other one for a hundred?

3
00:00:10,182 --> 00:00:13,085
[Value Added Reality]

4
00:00:13,085 --> 00:00:16,871
So those who are "subjective experts",

5
00:00:16,871 --> 00:00:22,459
they're determining value,
and they have some criteria for doing that.

6
00:00:22,459 --> 00:00:27,463
So in a similar way
we have to have some idea

7
00:00:27,463 --> 00:00:33,478
about what is that reality,
what is the nature of that reality

8
00:00:33,478 --> 00:00:37,757
who's going to express himself
through a particular agent.

9
00:00:37,757 --> 00:00:40,265
Is the Ultimate Reality

10
00:00:40,265 --> 00:00:43,207
something impersonal, abstract?

11
00:00:43,207 --> 00:00:44,639
Is it personal?

12
00:00:44,639 --> 00:00:46,415
Is it multi-dimensional?

13
00:00:46,415 --> 00:00:50,091
Can it be impersonal?

14
00:00:50,091 --> 00:00:53,237
Localized? And super-personal?

15
00:00:53,237 --> 00:00:58,342
All these things will have to be considered,
otherwise if we just say,

16
00:00:58,342 --> 00:01:03,841
"Well, it's some divine 
abstract thing that is moving me

17
00:01:03,841 --> 00:01:05,866
to express these things."

18
00:01:05,866 --> 00:01:08,001
How can that be verified?

19
00:01:08,001 --> 00:01:10,898
It all sounds good, then what is revealed?

20
00:01:10,898 --> 00:01:13,397
What is the substance of what is revealed?

21
00:01:13,397 --> 00:01:16,206
In Vedic culture,

22
00:01:16,206 --> 00:01:18,516
let's just put this out there also,

23
00:01:18,516 --> 00:01:24,996
visual arts are
in the lower section of society

24
00:01:24,996 --> 00:01:28,337
done by artisans and craftsmen.

25
00:01:29,097 --> 00:01:33,386
The higher section of society, brahmans,

26
00:01:33,386 --> 00:01:38,966
who are dealing with 
shabda-brahma, spiritual sound,

27
00:01:38,966 --> 00:01:46,423
they're not visual, they don't do
visual representations.

28
00:01:47,463 --> 00:01:51,866
The artist, the actor, all of those
positions in Vedic culture

29
00:01:51,866 --> 00:01:56,126
are in the lower section of society.

30
00:01:56,126 --> 00:01:57,427
Avadhut Maharaj: Why?

31
00:01:57,781 --> 00:02:01,280
Goswami Maharaj: I think, 
it's very obvious: because it's...

32
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,963
they are external.

